data.description: MOVE-IN READY, JUST LIKE THE MODEL! WITH LOTS OF UPGRADES, FEATURING 2 MASTER SUITES, 4 BEDROOMS AND AN OFFICE. LOCATED IN BEAUTIFUL ENCHANTED HILLS WITH A WONDERFUL BACK YARD AND A STUNNING VIEW OF THE MOUNTAINS. EXCELLENT CURB APPEAL WITH SPECIAL EASY CARE LANDSCAPING AND A WONDERFUL COVERED FRONT PORCH TO SIT AND ENJOY THE VIEWS AND VISITS WITH FRIENDLY NEIGHBORS. THE OFFICE OR SITTING ROOM HAS FRENCH DOORS FOR QUIET. THE MAIN LIVING AREA IS OPEN TO THE WONDERFUL KITCHEN WITH DOUBLE OVENS, STAINLESS APPLIANCES WITH REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED.THE LIVING AREA FEATURES A BEAUTIFUL STONE FIREPLACE. THE DOWNSTAIRS MASTER HAS A LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET AND PLENTY OF STORAGE. UPSTAIRS IS A BEAUTIFUL LOT AREA FOR A SECOND LIVING ROOM, THEN SURPRISE! ANOTHER MASTER BEDROOM. THE NAME OF THIS PLAN IS THE PARKER II AND YOU ARE GOING TO LOVE IT!
data.whatILove: A BEAUTIFULLY LANDSCAPED BACKYARD WITH A LOVELY VIEW OF THE FRANKLIN MOUNTAINS. QUIET COMMUNITY WITH PLENTY OF NEARBY WALKING/RUNNNG PATHS.  GREAT NEIGHBORS! AWESOME PLACE TO LIVE. PLENTY OF ROOM FOR GUESTS AND FAMILY VISITS. MAIN LEVEL LIVING WITH SPACIOUS KITCHEN / GREAT ROOM AREA AND ONE OF TWO MASTER BEDROOMS PLUS AN OFFICE. CLOSE TO HOSPITAL, OUTLET MALL AND I-10.
